data.title: 1982 Charlene – I’ve Never Been To Me
data.meta_description: I've Never Been to Me is an album by singer Charlene, released in 1982 on Motown. Charlene (born June 1, 1950, as Charlene Marilynn D'Angelo; married name Charlene Oliver) is an American easy-listening and R&B singer known mainly for her 1982 popular song "I've Never Been to Me". Tracks 1 I've Never Been To Me
data.text:
I’ve Never Been to Me is an album by singer Charlene, released in 1982 on Motown.

Charlene (born June 1, 1950, as Charlene Marilynn D’Angelo; married name Charlene Oliver) is an American easy-listening and R&B singer known mainly for her 1982 popular song “I’ve Never Been to Me”.
